{"tid":1853080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前帥評新魔般奴：全能到仆街","createTime":"2020-01-30T18:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T02:33:23.000Z","uid":209679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"eb5137b2a4ade100c2ee11658958bb0b96d7a947","tid":1853080,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:26:05.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】般奴費蘭迪斯加盟曼聯，曾在烏甸尼斯合作過的教練古杜連大讚他是全能中場。<br />\n<br />\n般奴費蘭迪斯（Bruno Fernandes）在士砵亭成名前，曾在意大利球壇征戰多年。古杜連（Francesco Guidolin）是他口中所說「在意大利其中一名對我影響最深的教練。」<br />\n<br />\n古杜連這樣評價舊部：「曼聯作出了非常重要的收購。他是金童，永遠都會挺身而出，而且球商極高。他很聰明、快速，跟隊友溝通很好。他跟我時常談話，我很高興他說我是在意大利最好的教練。」<br />\n<br />\n至於在新東家的前途，古杜連認為他的最佳位置是中場中：「對我來說，般奴是box-to-box中場，他不會有困難。他跟英超是完美的結合，因為英國球壇喜歡既技術且高速的球員，他是全能中場。」"},{"pid":"09f0e6a53ee53a37f3b514832187d7f983603360","tid":1853080,"uid":209679,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEsHfZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEsHfZH.png&h=c9a7c248&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b839df5d215de5100c89ee865cdb3bab7bb6410","tid":1853080,"uid":273774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09f0e6a53ee53a37f3b514832187d7f983603360","tid":1853080,"uid":209679,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEsHfZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEsHfZH.png&h=c9a7c248&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"bin到2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ccafde42b7d9bc8028bd6aa91b9108a3889aa00","tid":1853080,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6be0fd7638334e7d64267f793bd4a0c184fd473","tid":1853080,"uid":209679,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"